# Sign up for a free, 120 day Snowflake trial account

Use the link below to create your free, 120 day trial account:
https://signup.snowflake.com/?trial=student&cloud=aws&region=us-west-2&utm_source=coursera&utm_campaign=genai1

If you prefer to use an existing Snowflake account to complete the course, note that you may not be able to complete specific operations or exercises, 
especially if your existing account does not have ACCOUNTADMIN privileges. 

Also, not all the features required for this course are available in all regions.
If you want to try using your own Snowflake account, please select aws-us-west-2 region for the entirety of the course.
